# ChangeLog for sci-astronomy/atnf-miriad
# Copyright 1999-2008 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: $

  30 Mar 2008; Joshua Rich <joshua.rich@gmail.com> ChangeLog:
  Version bump, updated SRC_URI. Other cosmetic modifications to ebuild.

  08 Feb 2008; Joshua Rich <joshua@mso.anu.edu.au> ChangeLog:
  New ebuild that contains all current updates in SRC_URI, rather than
  	hacking up a 'live' ebuild.  So the version number is simply the
  	greatest MIRIAD update available at time of creation.

  07 Feb 2008; Joshua Rich <joshua@mso.anu.edu.au> ChangeLog:
  Edited configure.ac to use shared rpfits library if installed.

  05 Feb 2008; Joshua Rich <joshua@mso.anu.edu.au> ChangeLog:
  Fixed issue with configure failing to find installed PGPLOT library due to
  	'--as-needed' LDFLAG set.

  04 Feb 2008; Joshua Rich <joshua@mso.anu.edu.au> ChangeLog:
  Working 'live' ebuild for atnf-miriad.  Uses a custom function to check
  	for updates from the ATNF website, as they do not use a well-used
  	 method for providing updates.

*atnf-miriad-2007.1 (09 May 2007)

  09 May 2007; Joshua Rich joshua@mso.anu.edu.au
  Initial import.  Ebuild submitted by Joshua Rich joshua@mso.anu.edu.au
 
